{"tw": {"2066980": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Summer For You", "steam_appid": 2066980, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [3213510, 3213520, 3213530, 3213500], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/d40f46195124b808754a977cff0dc4b3.webp?t=1762822391\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/d40f46195124b808754a977cff0dc4b3.poster.avif?t=1762822391\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=483 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/eb641c056aba7fd49179eb45b8d2ea52.webp?t=1762822391\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/eb641c056aba7fd49179eb45b8d2ea52.poster.avif?t=1762822391\" class=\"bb_img\" width=620 height=298 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/04bd50eb04a104017c124ab5b2d96112.poster.avif?t=1762822391\" width=620 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/04bd50eb04a104017c124ab5b2d96112.webm?t=1762822391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/14f4a04da03df014777b2c8d55e8d5c3.poster.avif?t=1762822391\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/14f4a04da03df014777b2c8d55e8d5c3.webm?t=1762822391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/5371506bb00f16fb78c7ad4824fb3116.avif?t=1762822391\" width=617 height=159 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是位母胎單身21年的小處男，可父親卻是位受人景仰的考古學家。在耳濡目染之下，你日常也喜歡擺弄古董。有一天，你在父親的房間裏觸碰了一顆奇特的寶石，強大的魅魔哈莉奎娜隨即出現，她威脅要把你帶入地獄！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/1d77a9f08606b94b598d38c84a802f81.avif?t=1762822391\" width=614 height=211 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，女巫艾麗西亞及時出現並救下了你。她促使你和魅魔之間達成了協議。作為交換，你需要在兩周的時間內找到女友，並探尋人生的第一次是何種滋味……你只在電腦上談過戀愛，想要找個貨真價實的女朋友可絕非易事。調情、送禮物、推進關係，你得讓她們儘快愛上你。否則，等待你的將是魅魔與地獄無盡的火焰！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/7edd7ff8bee4c4a192c44d1c8e1e743c.avif?t=1762822391\" width=614 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲中包含有多種小遊戲來幫助你完成任務。首先，你得學會聊天。你可以向女孩提問以打聽她們的喜好，也可以展示學識和魅力來吸引她們。如果你有幸拿到了對方的電話號碼，那麼你還能通過短信與她來增進感情。此外，你還有本日記，用來記錄所有女孩的喜好。當被可愛的妹子環繞時，想要保持頭腦清醒可不容易……</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >時間不等人，趕緊行動起來，去贏得女孩們的芳心吧！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/e68a1dba8bc535f4d2b05ade7f0d4b8e.avif?t=1762822391\" width=614 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ 7位性感誘人的角色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ 5條獨立的故事線</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ 5種結局 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ 海量澀澀場景</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ 約會模擬器</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ 漫畫風格的對話系統</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ 豐富多彩的場景設計</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ 數種不同的迷你遊戲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p cla