team/apps/2066980/extras/4ce03ca9830c0f1e216a331c63d98e18.avif?t=1762822391\" width=620 height=331 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/80a2e6130dbc31bbfe0a368c9fcc38ef.avif?t=1762822391\" width=620 height=331 /></span></p>", "short_description": "《夏日風情》是一款熱辣火爆的2D視覺小說遊戲。在本作中，你可以運用多種遊戲機制來贏得女孩們的芳心！你是要廣開後宮，還是要追尋靈魂伴侶？你是要踏上救贖之旅，還是永墮魅魔的地獄？一切的一切，都盡在你的掌握之中！", "supported_languages": "英文, 俄文, 西班牙文 - 拉丁美洲, 簡體中文, 荷蘭文, 波蘭文, 土耳其文, 法文, 德文, 葡萄牙文 - 巴西, 繁體中文, 韓文, 泰文, 烏克蘭文, 日文, 義大利文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/header.jpg?t=1762822391", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/a914229c243145f61c32f7c34067803eb5ac6485/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1762822391", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/a914229c243145f61c32f7c34067803eb5ac6485/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1762822391", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 or later (x64)<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> 2,0 GHz Core 2 Duo<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 6 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Intel(R) HD Graphics 612<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：10<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "developers": ["AniCore Team"], "publishers": ["AniCore Team"], "price_overview": {"