04bd50eb04a104017c124ab5b2d96112.webm?t=1762822391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/14f4a04da03df014777b2c8d55e8d5c3.poster.avif?t=1762822391\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/14f4a04da03df014777b2c8d55e8d5c3.webm?t=1762822391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/5371506bb00f16fb78c7ad4824fb3116.avif?t=1762822391\" width=617 height=159 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re a 21-year old man who never had any relationships, but thanks to your archaeologist father you could enjoy your hobby - collecting ancient artifacts. Once, you touch a strange gem in your father’s room, and a powerful demoness Arlecchino appears, threatening to take you to Hell with her!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/1d77a9f08606b94b598d38c84a802f81.avif?t=1762822391\" width=614 height=211 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, thanks to Alicia, a powerful witch, you managed to strike a deal with the demoness - you have two weeks to find yourself a girlfriend and lose your virginity with her… Finding a girlfriend is hard when you’ve only romanced them in video games. Flirt, give them gifts and improve your relations. Make them fall in love with you or burn in Hell!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/7edd7ff8bee4c4a192c44d1c8e1e743c.avif?t=1762822391\" width=614 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll have a handful of mini-games to manage this task. First, make small talk, find out more about her and charm her with your erudition and insight in the style of a quiz. This won’t have to be in-person - if you get her number, you’ll have more chances talking with this beauty via messenger. Second, there’s a diary, where you note all the girls’ likes and dislikes. It’s hard thinking straight when there’s so many cute girls around…</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Time is not on your side, so start winning girls’ hearts right now!</strong><br><br></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/e68a1dba8bc535f4d2b05ade7f0d4b8e.avif?t=1762822391\" width=614 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ Sexy and unique characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ 5 separate storylines</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ 5 non-repetitive endings </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ High quality animated H-scenes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ Dating simulator</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ A dialogue system with comics-style overlay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ Colorful locations</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✌️ Several different mini-games</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/1a6e61a5835cc1057855df6363576480.avif?t=1762822391\" width=620 height=331 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066980/extras/b4c23e20e6edd5b7f5a58ba8c51403ed.avif?t=1762822391\" width=620 height=331 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img